declaration : VAR IDENTIFIER ASSIGN statement
            : OPEN_SCOPE block CLOSE_SCOPE

statement   : FUNCTION IDENTIFIER LPAREN IDENTIFIER[] RPAREN declaration
            : IF expression declaration (ELSE (IF expression declaration)* declaration)*

expression : comparison (AND | OR) comparison

comparison : not comparison
           : term (EQUALS | GREATER THAN | LESS THAN | GREATER OR EQUALS THAN | LESSER OR EQUALS THAN) comparsion

term : factor (PLUS | MINUS) factor

factor : unary (SLASH | STAR) factor

unary : (MINUS | NEGATION) call

call : atom ((LPAREN statement[] RPAREN) | (DOT IDENTIFIER))

atom : NUMBER
     : STRING
     : BOOLEAN
     : NULL
     : LPAREN expression RPAREN
     : VARIABLE